    "EvaluationThe performance of the approach was tested with different LLMs, data sets and settings as described in the following: Language modelsA variety of different models were tested.",
    "To investigate the approach with different LLMs (that are also diverse regarding design and training data), the following four models were used in the experiments:• FlanT5-XXL (FlanT5)is an LLM developed by Google Research.",
    "It's a variant of the T5 (text-to-text) model, that utilizes a unified text-to-text framework allowing it to perform a wide range of NLP tasks with the same model architecture, loss function, and hyperparameters.",
